  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then I found out when the place when I was hiding what was a very good place, the dogs were going with Amon Goeth through the street will smell me out because they smell at about 300 meter away a woman with child, and they kill them.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I stepped out from behind, and I pretend that I didn't see them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I start to move the bundles while people left, and they were sent to the Plaszow already or to Auschwitz-- because they separated one to go to Plaszow and the one to go to the-- to Auschwitz, you know?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when they came close to me-- I still have my boots and my breeches-- I click, report to him military way that I got the order from another officer to clean the road.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they start to laughing because it was a stupid order, but he was a officer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have a wonderful article written by American major, Air Force major, what means salute?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's respect to the superior, and superior will obey what you have to say it to him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the plot was working very good because I knew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Besides, I was watching he, too, what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he will go for gun, probably I will go for his throat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because nothing to lose anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was watching him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were laughing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He hit me with a right punch and said, verschwindet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This mean, get lost.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I salute again, click my heels, turned, and slowly I was going away till the next corner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I run when he couldn't see me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES] When I will be running, he will shoot me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mila was already-- what happened-- we make arrangement with Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
